Changelog
 
* Improved support for logo in the toolbar for the community sponsor - currently the old shapado blob way
* Extended doctype model to include create_button_label and create_help_text, this affects the create buttons and the create page
* Improved layout of the create page
* Further enhancements to the messaging templates, added a messaging management section to the community admin



