* Fixed 'My profile link throws hard error'
* Fixed messaging setting page in member settings (SS)
* Fixed the bug where posts with answers throw NameError in Items#show (SK)
* Fixed Sponsor Box title in Admin (SP)
* Minor fixes to page titles - notably removed users email from member page!

